Let them relax, just have to wait to receive the money.

563
00:33:28,160 --> 00:33:31,680
Besides, my family is not as warm as yours.

564
00:33:36,960 --> 00:33:37,680
Too much.

565
00:33:38,720 --> 00:33:40,180
I'll just handle it myself.

566
00:33:40,640 --> 00:33:43,500
If you mess up, you'll probably just get scolded.

567
00:33:49,360 --> 00:33:50,820
I can be a manager.

568
00:33:52,280 --> 00:33:54,210
But, can only be a manager.

569
00:33:54,920 --> 00:33:57,200
There can be no other relationship.

570
00:34:06,120 --> 00:34:06,960
Why?

571
00:34:08,600 --> 00:34:09,679
What do you mean?

572
00:34:10,060 --> 00:34:12,040
That is, we will not sleep together,

573
00:34:12,040 --> 00:34:13,239
won't hug,

574
00:34:13,239 --> 00:34:14,239
not kissing,

575
00:34:14,630 --> 00:34:16,460
there is no physical contact whatsoever.

576
00:34:19,139 --> 00:34:22,750
But, you can get a salary and you can have me.

577
00:34:24,750 --> 00:34:26,750
Be a little professional.

578
00:34:27,320 --> 00:34:28,850
Do you actually want to or not?

579
00:34:30,639 --> 00:34:31,360
Too much.

580
00:34:31,679 --> 00:34:33,409
Just do what you say.

581
00:34:33,560 --> 00:34:36,690
After all, you will change your mind sooner or later.

582
00:34:49,590 --> 00:34:51,120
Get out, I don't want it anymore.

583
00:34:52,880 --> 00:34:54,480
I haven't hired you yet.

584
00:34:54,520 --> 00:34:56,650
Don't rush to resign.

585
00:34:56,800 --> 00:34:59,440
♪ I'm forever yours ♪

586
00:34:59,600 --> 00:35:02,560
♪ Only you, this is real ♪

587
00:35:02,720 --> 00:35:07,400
♪ All my life and my whole heart is yours ♪

588
00:35:07,480 --> 00:35:09,960
♪ You are that person ♪

589
00:35:10,120 --> 00:35:12,800
♪ Stand before me ♪

590
00:35:13,000 --> 00:35:16,440
♪ It doesn't matter when I'm awake or in a dream ♪

591
00:35:16,520 --> 00:35:20,240
♪ I'm so happy that person is you ♪

592
00:35:20,310 --> 00:35:21,770
This is not the final version yet.

593
00:35:22,350 --> 00:35:24,520
What do you think after seeing it?

594
00:35:24,520 --> 00:35:26,380
This is clearly our life.

595
00:35:26,520 --> 00:35:28,850
You still dared to say no at that time.

596
00:35:29,760 --> 00:35:31,220
Because every one of my works

597
00:35:31,410 --> 00:35:33,280
all the material comes from you.

598
00:35:40,480 --> 00:35:42,760
Be it sad or happy,

599
00:35:45,120 --> 00:35:46,960
you are always in my story.

600
00:35:57,760 --> 00:35:58,560
Look.

601
00:36:00,840 --> 00:36:02,480
What's this? So cute.

602
00:36:04,700 --> 00:36:06,680
Do you remember the day we broke up?

603
00:36:07,200 --> 00:36:08,240
Your birthday.

604
00:36:09,320 --> 00:36:10,680
I prepared this.

605
00:36:11,090 --> 00:36:12,960
But, in the end it was not given.

606
00:36:15,160 --> 00:36:16,820
I saw it was a small deer.

607
00:36:16,880 --> 00:36:18,210
So, I remember you.

608
00:36:19,000 --> 00:36:20,760
Although it's not an expensive item.

609
00:36:22,200 --> 00:36:25,480
Maybe you don't need it anyway, so just save it.

610
00:36:25,480 --> 00:36:26,480
Why?

611
00:36:26,880 --> 00:36:27,960
So cute.

612
00:36:29,800 --> 00:36:31,480
Your gift

613
00:36:32,040 --> 00:36:33,770
not related to price.

614
00:36:34,560 --> 00:36:37,220
It becomes valuable because you think of me.

615
00:36:38,120 --> 00:36:39,780
Look, it looks like me, doesn't it?

616
00:36:42,880 --> 00:36:43,680
Like it or not?

617
00:36:43,960 --> 00:36:44,680
Of.

618
00:36:53,040 --> 00:36:57,440
Maybe I can't immediately change myself for you.

619
00:36:59,400 --> 00:37:02,860
But, I will try so that your heart is not too tired anymore.

620
00:37:05,520 --> 00:37:07,850
You don't need to change yourself, Bambi.

621
00:37:08,200 --> 00:37:11,260
Just communicate with me more if there are problems.

622
00:37:13,370 --> 00:37:14,760
There's one more thing.

623
00:37:15,400 --> 00:37:18,000
You don't need to try to make me happy.

624
00:37:19,200 --> 00:37:21,280
Because we should be happy together.

625
00:37:21,840 --> 00:37:22,600
Understand?

626
00:37:26,160 --> 00:37:26,960
I understand.

627
00:37:31,270 --> 00:37:33,480
Auntie can see it later.

628
00:37:33,680 --> 00:37:34,400
What is it?

629
00:37:34,520 --> 00:37:35,640
This is my house.

630
00:37:35,640 --> 00:37:37,240
I can do anything.

631
00:37:40,080 --> 00:37:41,540
You said it yourself.

632
00:37:49,000 --> 00:37:50,720
Do you like it or not, Little Bambi?

633
00:37:51,360 --> 00:37:52,560
Really like it.

634
00:37:52,960 --> 00:37:55,560
Look, you can still put things in it.

635
00:38:00,210 --> 00:38:03,480
Can this contain the love I give you?

636
00:38:09,760 --> 00:38:10,960
You're so cute.

637
00:38:12,120 --> 00:38:13,080
Thank You.

638
00:38:13,440 --> 00:38:14,760
I really like.

639
00:38:18,490 --> 00:38:20,600
This is Fiona's business proposal.

640
00:38:20,640 --> 00:38:23,360
It focuses on different customers than the main brand.

641
00:38:23,360 --> 00:38:26,760
Next, it will launch a whole series of bags and shoes.

642
00:38:27,500 --> 00:38:29,900
However, his style is definitely different from Yanin's.

643
00:38:30,520 --> 00:38:32,840
Did you do all this yourself?

644
00:38:32,840 --> 00:38:33,960
Of.

645
