647
00:38:42,080 --> 00:38:43,600
I'll consider it first.

648
00:38:45,160 --> 00:38:47,320
But, you have to consistently do it.

649
00:38:47,320 --> 00:38:49,280
This is not a toy that can be thrown away if you get bored.

650
00:38:49,280 --> 00:38:51,140
Have to invest millions of baht.

651
00:38:52,720 --> 00:38:53,680
Do you understand?

652
00:38:55,080 --> 00:38:58,160
I will not tarnish the reputation of your only daughter.

653
00:39:10,800 --> 00:39:11,760
Thank You.

654
00:39:21,010 --> 00:39:22,000
Become a wealthy woman.

655
00:39:22,000 --> 00:39:23,360
The money has been earned.

656
00:39:28,040 --> 00:39:29,160
Not rich yet.

657
00:39:29,370 --> 00:39:32,570
But, it's enough to take your girlfriend out for a big meal.

658
00:39:33,280 --> 00:39:36,040
Save the money first to buy things for the new house.

659
00:39:36,040 --> 00:39:37,680
No need to treat me to a meal.

660
00:39:37,680 --> 00:39:39,210
But, I want to take care of you.

661
00:39:39,480 --> 00:39:40,740
Because I'm already dating,

662
00:39:40,840 --> 00:39:42,480
must look after each other.

663
00:39:42,840 --> 00:39:45,520
How is it okay to always let you take care of me alone?

664
00:39:45,520 --> 00:39:47,080
I'm just worried about you.

665
00:39:47,440 --> 00:39:50,040
You need money for many other important things.

666
00:39:50,640 --> 00:39:52,400
Don't always act like a big brother.

667
00:39:52,400 --> 00:39:54,460
It's okay to act like a boyfriend.

668
00:39:54,890 --> 00:39:56,760
I'm being a girlfriend.

669
00:39:56,970 --> 00:40:00,630
Because I'm your boyfriend, I should help you with your finances.

670
00:40:06,600 --> 00:40:07,480
What do you want?

671
00:40:08,360 --> 00:40:09,040
Preaw.

672
00:40:10,680 --> 00:40:12,160
People can see it later.

673
00:40:12,880 --> 00:40:14,880
Aren't couples just like this?

674
00:40:14,880 --> 00:40:16,400
Don't just talk.

675
00:40:16,400 --> 00:40:18,160
Must act.

676
00:40:18,840 --> 00:40:19,480
Preaw.

677
00:40:20,480 --> 00:40:21,120
Preaw.

678
00:40:21,120 --> 00:40:22,240
Pleases me.

679
00:40:23,160 --> 00:40:23,600
Preaw.

680
00:40:23,640 --> 00:40:24,840
Sis Min, I have...

681
00:40:29,840 --> 00:40:30,880
Sorry.

682
00:40:31,240 --> 00:40:32,570
I'll come back later.

683
00:40:38,160 --> 00:40:40,960
I told you not to be like this in the company.

684
00:40:42,800 --> 00:40:45,000
But, you are the boss in this company.

685
00:40:45,000 --> 00:40:48,260
After all, most people here like women too.

686
00:40:48,440 --> 00:40:49,680
What are you afraid of?

687
00:40:50,850 --> 00:40:53,510
That's true, but I have to maintain my image.

688
00:40:54,790 --> 00:40:57,680
Sis, are you sure it's just for image?

689
00:40:59,000 --> 00:41:01,190
Don't you want to publish me?

690
00:41:01,190 --> 00:41:02,480
Not like that.

691
00:41:03,600 --> 00:41:04,960
This takes time.

692
00:41:07,160 --> 00:41:09,560
Don't let today be too long, Sis.

693
00:41:11,120 --> 00:41:13,580
I feel like a secret lover now.

694
00:41:26,950 --> 00:41:29,010
My mother is preparing to open a shop for me.

695
00:41:30,530 --> 00:41:33,000
Then, it will continue to expand its branches slowly.

696
00:41:33,000 --> 00:41:34,290
After stabilizing in the market,

697
00:41:34,290 --> 00:41:36,550
then opened branches abroad.

698
00:41:38,080 --> 00:41:39,400
Sounds really great.

699
00:41:39,400 --> 00:41:41,260
But, maybe you will be very tired.

700
00:41:43,400 --> 00:41:44,730
But, if you are serious,

701
00:41:45,280 --> 00:41:48,680
I think you can definitely reach international standards.

702
00:41:50,800 --> 00:41:51,560
But,

703
00:41:52,400 --> 00:41:55,730
maybe we can't see each other often for a while.

704
00:41:57,520 --> 00:41:58,960
I'll be very busy.

705
00:42:00,960 --> 00:42:02,960
Besides, I want to stop partying.

706
00:42:02,960 --> 00:42:04,760
So you can focus on this.

707
00:42:05,560 --> 00:42:08,360
I have to prove myself to my mother and you.

708
00:42:13,280 --> 00:42:14,360
No need.

709
00:42:14,960 --> 00:42:16,820
I always knew you were serious.

710
00:42:19,040 --> 00:42:21,160
Just say if you need help.

711
00:42:23,960 --> 00:42:26,560
I want your dreams to come true.

712
00:42:28,040 --> 00:42:30,310
Just like you who continued to support me at that time.

713
00:42:30,310 --> 00:42:33,110
Until I can open this production company.

714
00:42:35,640 --> 00:42:36,760
So,

715
00:42:38,080 --> 00:42:41,880
You don't plan on giving a reward to the person who made this effort?

716
00:42:48,600 --> 00:42:49,400
Just like this?

717
00:42:50,400 --> 00:42:52,730
This is just a "deposit" paid up front.

718
00:42:54,320 --> 00:42:55,240
So,

719
00:42:56,440 --> 00:42:58,900
don't you want a “deposit”?

720
00:43:00,120 --> 00:43:02,560
No way, there's still an interview later.

721
00:43:02,560 --> 00:43:04,290
Just let them wait.

722
00:43:14,040 --> 00:43:14,760
Too much?

723
00:43:15,680 --> 00:43:18,140
We will continue after the interview is finished.

724
00:43:19,880 --> 00:43:20,840
Too much?

725
00:43:24,240 --> 00:43:24,960
Good.

726
00:43:26,640 --> 00:43:27,770
See you later.

727
00:43:41,860 --> 00:43:42,880
Bambi.

728
00:43:48,680 --> 00:43:49,740
It's really you.

729
00:43:50,120 --> 00:43:51,250
Do you still remember me?

730
00:43:51,280 --> 00:43:53,610
We met on the badminton court.

731
00:43:54,840 --> 00:43:56,770
Remember your face, but forget your name.

732
00:43:57,040 --> 00:43:58,360
My name is Aerie.

733
00:43:59,760 --> 00:44:01,360
Oh, Aerie.

734
00:44:02,800 --> 00:44:04,460
What did you come here for?

735
00:44:04,790 --> 00:44:06,560
I applied for a job here.

736
00:44:07,200 --> 00:44:09,960
You came to look for Sis Prim, right?

737
00:44:15,180 --> 00:44:17,510
How did you know Prim works here?

738
00:44:18,360 --> 00:44:20,160
When we met that day,

739
00:44:20,240 --> 00:44:22,360
I checked Sis Prim's social account.

740
00:44:22,400 --> 00:44:23,370
I just found out

741
00:44:23,370 --> 00:44:27,610
he is the director of several MVs and commercials that I really like.

742
00:44:28,040 --> 00:44:29,750
So, I applied for a job here.

743
00:44:29,750 --> 00:44:31,960
Want to work with great people.

744
00:44:33,360 --> 00:44:34,690
Wish you luck.

745
00:44:35,400 --> 00:44:36,200
Thank You.

746
00:44:39,720 --> 00:44:40,480
Bambi.

747
00:44:48,800 --> 00:44:50,060
This shirt is very nice.

748
00:44:50,120 --> 00:44:51,160
What's the brand?

749
00:44:54,200 --> 00:44:55,160
Fiona.

750
00:44:55,800 --> 00:44:56,800
My own brand.

751
00:45:04,520 --> 00:45:06,160
I'll buy it too.

752
00:45:06,400 --> 00:45:08,660
Maybe I could be beautiful like you.

753
00:45:17,120 --> 00:45:19,400
It was unexpected that we could meet here.

754
00:45:19,400 --> 00:45:20,530
What a coincidence.

755
00:45:20,990 --> 00:45:22,720
That timing was just a coincidence.

756
00:45:22,760 --> 00:45:24,220
But, this time it was intentional.

757
00:45:24,320 --> 00:45:26,080
I want this job.

758
00:45:26,080 --> 00:45:28,160
So, why apply for a job at Lady Bird?

759
00:45:28,160 --> 00:45:30,480
We are just a small production company.

760
00:45:32,960 --> 00:45:34,280
I like Sis Prim.

761
00:45:41,200 --> 00:45:44,720
Eh, I mean I like Kak Prim's work.

762
00:45:44,760 --> 00:45:46,090
Not like that.

763
00:45:47,000 --> 00:45:48,120
Startled me.

764
00:45:48,440 --> 00:45:50,560
I guess expressing feelings.

765
00:45:50,800 --> 00:45:53,280
Actually, I secretly found out.

766
00:45:53,640 --> 00:45:55,140
I know Sis Prim and Sis Min

767
00:45:55,140 --> 00:45:58,040
opened this company to make women's work.

768
00:45:58,040 --> 00:46:00,680
Additionally, most of the employees here are women.

769
00:46:00,680 --> 00:46:01,940
Because Sis Prim feels

770
00:46:02,030 --> 00:46:05,160
women don't get many opportunities in this field.

771
00:46:06,400 --> 00:46:08,660
Really looking for good information.

772
00:46:08,680 --> 00:46:10,760
It's estimated that everyone has been interviewed, right?

773
00:46:10,760 --> 00:46:13,390
Don't say it is the fans who come to chase the artist.

774
00:46:13,390 --> 00:46:15,130
Oh, no.

775
00:46:15,240 --> 00:46:17,040
I just focus on work.

776
00:46:17,160 --> 00:46:18,960
Guaranteed there is no personal intention.

777
00:46:21,520 --> 00:46:23,450
Your resume looks very good.

778
00:46:23,480 --> 00:46:25,480
I think we can work together.

779
00:46:26,360 --> 00:46:28,160
I will not disappoint you.

780
00:46:38,960 --> 00:46:40,960
Why come to the furniture store?

781
00:46:41,000 --> 00:46:42,520
Is there work here?

782
00:46:42,520 --> 00:46:43,360
There isn't any.

783
00:46:43,440 --> 00:46:44,840
Just walking around.

784
00:46:45,480 --> 00:46:46,160
Ha?

785
00:46:47,520 --> 00:46:49,190
Then, why did you bring me here?

786
00:46:49,190 --> 00:46:51,050
I have to take care of other things too.

787
00:46:51,720 --> 00:46:52,720
What do you want to take care of?

788
00:46:52,760 --> 00:46:53,680
Try saying it.

789
00:46:56,760 --> 00:46:57,960
Can't answer.

790
00:46:57,960 --> 00:46:59,520
That means it's not that important.

791
00:46:59,520 --> 00:47:01,280
Just come around with me.

792
00:47:01,280 --> 00:47:02,520
As a manager,

793
00:47:02,560 --> 00:47:04,820
You must understand me deeply.

794
00:47:59,440 --> 00:48:01,960
You know? I could be here all day.

795
00:48:02,380 --> 00:48:04,610
Every time I touch this used thing,

796
00:48:04,610 --> 00:48:07,650
I can always imagine that old family.

797
00:48:08,170 --> 00:48:11,970
For example, the dining table that was once used by parents and children.

798
00:48:12,360 --> 00:48:13,760
Looks very warm.

799
00:48:17,720 --> 00:48:19,560
Then, why don't you buy a house?

800
00:48:19,560 --> 00:48:22,360
This way there is space to put furniture.

801
00:48:22,360 --> 00:48:23,620
Why buy it?

802
00:48:23,820 --> 00:48:26,350
After all, it will end up being left alone.

803
00:48:26,400 --> 00:48:30,200
Ha? Your family doesn't come home and live with you?

804
00:48:32,360 --> 00:48:33,360
What family?

805
00:48:33,900 --> 00:48:35,760
My mother already has a new family.

806
00:48:36,800 --> 00:48:40,060
Now, I just need to work and send money.

807
00:48:41,380 --> 00:48:42,910
Sometimes, I wonder too.

808
00:48:43,240 --> 00:48:45,500
What am I actually working hard for?

809
00:48:45,770 --> 00:48:48,200
In order to buy pleasure for yourself.

810
00:48:48,200 --> 00:48:51,040
Now, the single rate is getting higher.

811
00:48:51,340 --> 00:48:53,040
The birth rate is getting lower.

812
00:48:53,040 --> 00:48:55,240
Almost everyone in this world is single.

813
00:48:56,140 --> 00:48:57,670
Then, you want to be single?

814
00:48:58,720 --> 00:49:00,760
Single or not.

815
00:49:02,820 --> 00:49:05,490
But, seeing his parents making out in the kitchen,

816
00:49:05,570 --> 00:49:06,770
really very cute.

817
00:49:07,520 --> 00:49:10,280
Once, their "main topic" of the day

818
00:49:10,320 --> 00:49:12,720
is to put capri beans in phat kaphrao or not.

819
00:49:12,720 --> 00:49:14,840
There is one more thing that makes them fight a lot.

820
00:49:14,840 --> 00:49:17,570
Should you call it sambal fish or fish sauce?

821
00:49:17,800 --> 00:49:20,330
Fighting so childishly.

822
00:49:22,960 --> 00:49:25,040
I just want to have an atmosphere like that too.

823
00:49:25,040 --> 00:49:28,170
Anyone can fight with me over nonsense.

824
00:49:39,520 --> 00:49:41,380
I can accompany you to fight.

825
00:49:42,450 --> 00:49:43,480
Funny.

826
00:49:43,840 --> 00:49:46,170
Don't take advantage of the opportunity there.

827
00:49:46,520 --> 00:49:48,250
Just seeing you so sad,

828
00:49:49,160 --> 00:49:51,090
want you to feel more meaningful.

829
00:49:52,320 --> 00:49:54,760
Is this what you say as a manager?

830
00:49:55,800 --> 00:49:56,560
Nope.

831
00:49:57,440 --> 00:50:00,900
I just feel sorry for a model who pretends to be lonely.

832
00:50:16,640 --> 00:50:17,360
What do you want?

833
00:50:17,680 --> 00:50:18,440
Dance.

834
00:50:19,400 --> 00:50:21,040
Dancing what? I want to go home.

835
00:50:21,040 --> 00:50:22,880
Come on, the atmosphere is right.

836
00:50:23,290 --> 00:50:24,280
Whose atmosphere?

837
00:50:24,640 --> 00:50:26,160
Your own atmosphere, right?

838
00:50:26,950 --> 00:50:27,680
Ayo.

839
